From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:28:44 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] clk: cix: Add ACPI clock infrastructure for CIX Sky1

Add Sky1 audio subsystem clock controller and ACPI clock
infrastructure including:
- sky1-audss: Audio subsystem clock and gate controller
- sky1-acpi: ACPI clock provider using CLKT consumer references
- clk-scmi ACPI enablement
- clkdev registration fix for ACPI consumers
